snippet.title: Covid-19: New Zealand to move to traffic light system from December 3 | Stuff
snippet.description:
Jacinda Ardern has confirmed New Zealand will enter the new traffic-light system on December 3, leaving the alert level system behind for good. Read more: https://bit.ly/30OOn80 | Subscribe to our channel: https://bit.ly/2JPg8oB
